OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey but humid morning
OL,6,Fwith some mist and murky near the
OL,7,Fcoasts and over the hills. Eastern
OL,8,Fareas though will see some sunshine
OL,9,Fdevelop, especially during the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Whereas outbreaks of rain
OL,11,Fwill spill into the west.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA warm evening with some late
OL,14,Fsunshine in the east, however cloud
OL,15,Fand rain in the west will spread
OL,16,Facross the country overnight. Another
OL,17,Fhumid night to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
