OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,6,Fspots of rain, especially over the
OL,7,Fhills. The cloud will break up
OL,8,Fthroughout the morning, leading to a
OL,9,Fmuch brighter afternoon. Feeling a tad
OL,10,Ffresher.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHigh
OL,13,Fpressure building bringing plenty of
OL,14,Fdry and sunny weather. Temperatures
OL,15,Fincreasing by day and night with hot
OL,16,Fand humid conditions developing which
OL,17,Fmay trigger a few showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
